# This project authenticates to Claude via the Claude CLI's stored OAuth login
# (~/.claude), NOT an API key. Run `claude login` once and you're set.
#
# The backend intentionally drops ANTHROPIC_API_KEY and ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN from
# the environment so the SDK-spawned `claude` CLI always uses OAuth. Setting an API
# key here has no effect.
#
# Optional overrides:
# DATABASE_PATH=backend/jobs.db
